## Finding Report Format

Use this format for every finding:

```
🔴 CRITICAL | 🟠 HIGH | 🟡 MEDIUM | 🔵 LOW | ⚪ INFO

[SEVERITY] [Framework ID] — Title
File: [filename], line [X]
Issue: [clear description of the vulnerability]
Impact: [specific attack scenario or compliance violation]
Fix:
  [exact corrected code or configuration]
References: [CVE / CWE / control ID]
```

**Severity definitions:**
- CRITICAL: Directly exploitable, data breach likely, regulatory fine probable
- HIGH: Exploitable with moderate effort or significant compliance gap
- MEDIUM: Exploitable under specific conditions or policy violation
- LOW: Defense-in-depth improvement, minor policy gap
- INFO: Best practice recommendation, no direct security impact

